{"tid":28334,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"只差18分鐘　美斯險遇墜機厄運","createTime":"2016-12-08T01:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T02:25:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a17782953740ae2b56649febbe3b80fafaaf4e9a","tid":28334,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:12:48.000Z","msg":"巴甲球會查比高恩斯的包機上周在哥倫比亞墜毀，震驚全球，事後有報道指阿根廷球王美斯（Lionel Messi）上月初搭過同一架機，更可怕的是，原來在該程裏客機也是瀕臨耗盡燃料邊緣，只差18分鐘就油盡，稍有差誤，美斯及其阿根廷隊友的命運難以想像。<br />\n<br />\n查比高恩斯職球員乘坐的玻利維亞拉米亞航空（LaMia）包機，因燃油耗盡墜毀，球會職球員等71人罹難。<br />\n<br />\n該「死亡客機」墜毀前兩周，曾經接載美斯、阿古路等阿根廷國家隊球員。他們作客巴西出席2018年俄羅斯世界盃外圍賽後，乘搭該機返回阿根廷。巴西一份報章報道，該機如果注滿燃料可飛4小時22分鐘，而由巴西貝洛奧里藏特（Belo Horizonte）飛往阿根廷布宜諾斯艾利斯，需時4小時4分鐘。換言之，客機差18分鐘就會油盡。<br />\n<br />\n不過，阿根廷當局堅稱客機燃料量足夠飛行4小時49分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56018561&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56018561%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161208&d=7Q37PLU0iRpdUxo743K20AT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=e495ffd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56018561%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161208&h=1f7589f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56018561&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161208</a>"},{"pid":"14946c92a0018ea58460cb5b31cc0fdc99435bfe","tid":28334,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e40a274f3cce095b42964b0656f73d4c77895e","tid":28334,"uid":1762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:50:53.000Z","msg":"美斯唔係坐私人飛機架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3704410778d0f5d38db29780fbb2919c7c002ece","tid":283